    "title": "Utajiri na Umaskini katika Fasihi ya Hekima",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "utajiri na umaskini katika fasihi ya hekima",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Methali katika Maandiko kuhusu utajiri na umaskini, hasa katika fasihi ya hekima, zinaonyesha ukweli mpana. Mungu huwabariki watu wenye hekima kwa utajiri, ambao hufanya changamoto za maisha kuwa rahisi kushughulikia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9-Prov3:10\">Mithali 3:9–10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:15-Prov3:16\">15–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:22\">10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:15\">10:15</a>). Tabia za kijinga, hasa uvivu, mara nyingi husababisha umaskini (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4\">10:4</a>).</p><p>Kitabu cha Mithali kinatambua kwamba baadhi ya watu waovu ambao ni wapumbavu ni matajiri, lakini kinatukumbusha kwamba utajiri huu hautadumu kwa muda mrefu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:18\">Mithali 11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:11\">13:11</a>). Umaskini wakati mwingine unaweza kusababishwa na ukosefu wa haki badala ya upumbavu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:23\">13:23</a>). Utajiri unaweza kutokana na ukosefu wa haki na udanganyifu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:8\">16:8</a>). Wale wenye utajiri wanahitaji kuutumia kwa busara, ikiwa ni pamoja na kuwa wakarimu kwa wale wanaohitaji (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:7\">29:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:14\">14</a>).</p><p>Utajiri una faida chache. Wakati mwingine, huleta matatizo badala ya kuyatatua (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:4\">Mithali 11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:8\">13:8</a>). Hekima inaweza kusaidia kwa njia ambazo utajiri hauwezi, na hivyo kufanya hekima kuwa muhimu zaidi kuliko pesa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:16-Prov15:17\">15:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:8\">16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:16\">16</a>).</p><p>Mungu mara nyingi huwabariki watu wanaoishi ili kumfurahisha kwa kuwapa wanachohitaji. Hii ikitokea, watu hawa wanaweza kusaidia wengine kwa kushiriki walichopokea. Kutoa kwa wengine ni baraka nyingine kutoka kwa Mungu. Hata hivyo, hali si kila mara ni za haki. Wakati mwingine, utajiri hauendi kwa wale wanaoustahili (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:11\">Mhubiri 9:11</a>). Hauleti furaha kila mara (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17-Eccl2:23\">Mhubiri 2:17–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10-Eccl5:17\">5:10–17</a>). Kwa kweli, pesa zinaweza kuharibu imani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1 Timotheo 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:13\">Yakobo 2:1–13</a>). Wakati wa kuchagua kati ya kuishi kumfurahisha Mungu na pesa, watu wenye busara watachagua kuishi kumfurahisha Mungu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:10-Deut6:13\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 6:10–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:10-Deut8:11\">8:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:7\">1 Samweli 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:16\">Zaburi 37:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9-Prov3:10\">Mithali 3:9–10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:15-Prov3:16\">15–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:15\">10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:22\">22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:4\">11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:18\">18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:8\">13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:11\">11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:24\">14:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:6\">15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:16-Prov15:17\">16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:8\">16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:16\">16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:4-Prov23:5\">23:4–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:7\">29:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:14\">14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10-Eccl5:17\">Mhubiri 5:10–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1 Timotheo 6:10</a></p>",
